text: Pachycormus is the scientific name for two animal genera: * Pachycormus (fish), an extinct genus of pachycormiform from the Jurassic * Pachycormus discolor, a genus of plants in the family Anacardiaceae This disambiguation page lists articles about distinct genera with the same name.
